text: Banco Supervielle is a commercial banking entity of Argentine origin, with headquarters in Buenos Aires. Supervielle arises from the merger of Banco Banex and Société Générale de Argentina. In 2004, Banco Banex bought the shares of Banco Société Générale de Argentina, and returned to the Supervielle brand, used until 1964. ==References== == Other websites == * Official website Category:1887 establishments Category:1880s establishments in Argentina Category:Companies based in Buenos Aires Category:Banks of Argentina
